101+ Funny & Clever Tech Team Names for Work and the Generators to Make Your Own

By  Syed Hammad Mahmood
Updated  Feb 7, 2023

Try something different:

Coming up with unique team names that reflect your team's identity can be a bit tricky. This is especially true if you are looking for some funny, clever names with a tech theme. Pretty niche, huh?

Here, we've rounded up eight tools for generating original, wacky tech team names. Using these tools, we created dozens of tech team names, which we list below.

1. EasyRetro Scrum Team Name Generator

EasyRetro is a retrospective tool that helps teams improve their work. In addition to other free tools, EasyRetro has a Scrum Team Name Generator.

This simple tech team name generator asks you a few questions and then suggests a suitable team name. You have to choose an adjective, letter, number, and color relevant to your team. Moreover, it asks for your usual sprint length.

While this tool isn't specifically designed for generating tech team names, it suggests some unique names that are ideal for technical teams. For example, check out the following names generated by this tool.

  1. Wonderful Null Set
  2. Hopeful Rifles
  3. Gracious Jesters
  4. Perfect Unit
  5. Quiet Band
  6. Intelligent Sonics
  7. Next-level Masters
  8. Fierce Cherubims
  9. Amped Ultras
  10. Loud Royals
  11. Beastly Pythons
  12. Legendary Lieutenants
  13. Smart Crew

2. Mountain Goat Software Agile Team Name Generator

This tool aims to provide a gnarly, wicked name for your agile team. Using a different approach than other name generator tools, it asks five questions about your team instead of a keyword.

Enter the first initial of your company or project and the floor where most of your members work. Next, it asks about your team's favorite ice cream flavor. In case you dont know, you can use these team feedback tools to decide.

Next, enter how you celebrated the team's latest victory and your sprint length. Finally, the tool comes up with funny, clever names that reflect your teams unique identity.

  1. Kickin Crew
  2. Filthy Fresh Brainiacs
  3. Noice Set
  4. Fierce Matrix
  5. Savage Squad
  6. Iconic Force
  7. Legendary Set
  8. Beastly Syndicate
  9. Spifftacular Troop
  10. Smooth Posse
  11. Choice Matrix
  12. Amped Null Set
  13. Notorious Squad

3. GoRetro Team Name Generator

GoRetro is a retro tool for agile teams. Its Team Name Generator provides random wacky names for tech teams. It doesnt ask for any input, and you can keep generating names until you find a suitable one.

The names are unique and creative, for example:

  1. Unbelievable Jargon
  2. Beige Panache
  3. Amazing Hashtag Wizards
  4. Freelance Analytics
  5. Diva Code
  6. Experienced Full-Stack
  7. BugSquashers
  8. Serene Server
  9. Plucky Wireframe
  10. Immutable Encryption
  11. Trouble Shouters
  12. Hugs for my Bugs
  13. The Rubix Cube
  14. Irregular QWERTY

4. Leadership Geeks Team Name Generator

Leadership Geeks has a simple team name generator on its site. The tool asks you to enter a word or two that describes your team. This can be anything from your teams project, favorite color, or just a random object you identify with.

But since the tool is not designed specifically for tech teams, so make sure to include some tech-related keywords. It basically adds a noun after the word youve entered. When we entered the word code, heres what we got:

  1. Code Cherubim
  2. Code New Town
  3. Code Magnum Force

It suggests one name at a time, but you can keep clicking on Go to get more names. Similarly, other names we got were:

  1. Techie Pythons
  2. IT Elites
  3. Network Knights
  4. Dev Kings
  5. Bug Slayers
  6. Data Sonic
  7. Byte Baal
  8. Android Alchemists
  9. Web Spirits
  10. Cloud Storms
  11. Bot Commandos

5. Masterpiece Generator Name Generator

Masterpiece Generator has a tool for generating fun and clever team names. It stands out from other tools as it doesnt ask for a keyword. Instead, you've to enter a color, some adjectives, a place, some animals, and a noun for a group of people. The tool can also fill all the fields with random suggestions.

Name Generator combines these words to create a quirky name for your team. If you want the name to reflect the geeky side of your team, youll have to enter related adjectives. Heres what we got from this tool.

  1. Simple Nerds
  2. Tech Nerds
  3. Sympathetic Dodgers
  4. Clumsy Coders
  5. Bit Developers
  6. Thoughtless Troubleshooters
  7. Coding Hamsters
  8. Techie Pythons
  9. Code Killer
  10. Patriotic Programmers
  11. Helpful Hackers
  12. Web Spiders

6. Wordlab Team Name Generator

Wordlab has several name generator tools on its site, including one for teams. Using this, you can get funny, unique names for your team. The names dont necessarily reflect the technical aspect of your team, but its spirit and identity.

Instead of asking for a prompt, it provides 20 random team names. However, you can keep generating new names until you find an ideal name. It suggests wacky, out-of-the-box names like:

  1. Awful Turtle Oracles
  2. Orange Death Nodes
  3. Lazy Red Banshees
  4. Black Sky Squad
  5. Prancing Land Logic
  6. The Endzone Giants
  7. The Foam Sharks
  8. The Laughing Damage
  9. Homeland Net Resistance
  10. Phat Lunatic Crawlers
  11. Choking Worm Spree
  12. The Streak Cyclops
  13. Extended Air Strikers

7. Namify Team Name Generator

As the name suggests, Namify is a smart online tool that generates names for almost anythingfrom your business and band names to DJ and crypto names.

Its Team Name Generator can generate clever names for your tech team. It asks you to enter a couple of keywords and provides hundreds of names. To filter out irrelevant ones, you can select categories like IT, Technology, AR, and AI.

Likewise, theres an option to filter names by prefix/suffix, number of words, character limit, etc. You can click on any name to check the domain and social media handle availability. Some of the names it suggested are:

  1. Techno Sync
  2. Cyborg Droids
  3. Cool Nerds
  4. Meta Workforce
  5. The Bot Project
  6. Byte Shift
  7. Core Chip
  8. Start Cyber
  9. Crypt Work
  10. Frontendify
  11. Bitium
  12. Nerds Logic
  13. Dotech

Besides this, it also has a Tech Company Name Generator, which suggests good names for teams as well.

8. BizNameWiz Generators

Being one of the most versatile business name generators, BizNameWiz has tools for various industries. Its Tech, Nerdy, and Geek Name Generator can suggest names for your tech teams.

Enter the keywords, and it instantly gives several names. You can apply filters, select industry, and check domain availability.

  1. Techlada
  2. Tactic Tech
  3. Dudes Team
  4. Techlance
  5. Technopolis
  6. Coders Breed

Similarly, its Data Analytics Company and Team Name Generator suggest names like:

  1. Misfit Tech
  2. Team Hex
  3. Developers Drive

And heres what the Software Company Name Generator suggested:

  1. Team Beta
  2. Tech Titan
  3. Coder Cookies
  4. Tec Nerds

Find a Funny Name for Your Tech Team

Whether you want a unique identity for your tech team or just a random name for a group activity, these tools can help you come up with wacky ones. Some of these tools provide random, clever suggestions, while others offer personalized team names.

Once you've found the perfect name for your team, online name generators can provide funny names for your team members as well.
